items.title: Shutting down dev.jspm.io after 10 years
items.content_html: With import maps successfully being supported natively, the JSPM project is moving to only support import map CDN workflows via the ga.jspm.io CDN, while jspm.dev & dev.jspm.io are being deprecated after 10 years of operation.
